name: Enlightment
description:
This is one of the series drawings, paintings and gifs of squarelooking characters I am working on. 
It reflects my feeling that our life is becoming more and more organazed, schedualed and structured and even geometrical so once people themselves will turn into restangulars or probably it's just my own fears, once after I accidently did spice I found myself in 2D world, it was so difficult to make moves and I was so afraid that I would stuck in 2D forever .
